```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Birthday Pop Animation</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:#ffdae8; /* pink theme */
font-family:Arial;
overflow:hidden;
}

.text{
font-size:70px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.text span{
display:inline-block;
transform:scale(0);
animation:pop 0.5s forwards;
}

/* delay for each letter */

.text span:nth-child(1){animation-delay:0s;color:#ff006e;}
.text span:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.1s;color:#ff4d6d;}
.text span:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.2s;color:#ff85a1;}
.text span:nth-child(4){animation-delay:0.3s;color:#ff9f1c;}
.text span:nth-child(5){animation-delay:0.4s;color:#8338ec;}
.text span:nth-child(6){animation-delay:0.5s;color:#ff006e;}
.text span:nth-child(7){animation-delay:0.6s;color:#ff4d6d;}
.text span:nth-child(8){animation-delay:0.7s;color:#ff85a1;}
.text span:nth-child(9){animation-delay:0.8s;color:#ff9f1c;}
.text span:nth-child(10){animation-delay:0.9s;color:#8338ec;}
.text span:nth-child(11){animation-delay:1s;color:#ff006e;}
.text span:nth-child(12){animation-delay:1.1s;color:#ff4d6d;}
.text span:nth-child(13){animation-delay:1.2s;color:#ff85a1;}

@keyframes pop{
0%{
transform:scale(0);
opacity:0;
}
70%{
transform:scale(1.3);
}
100%{
transform:scale(1);
opacity:1;
}
}

.bears{
position:absolute;
bottom:40px;
font-size:60px;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="text">
<span>H</span>
<span>A</span>
<span>P</span>
<span>P</span>
<span>Y</span>
<span>&nbsp;</span>
<span>B</span>
<span>I</span>
<span>R</span>
<span>T</span>
<span>H</span>
<span>D</span>
<span>A</span>
<span>Y</span>
</div>

<div class="bears">
🧸 💗 🧸
</div>

</body>
</html>
```